descriptionHtml:
Since nords are supposed to be \"big and burly\" as one of the devs said... It seemed kinda
weird. Men look like bodybuilders and \"ofcourse\" women look like playboy bunnies (with
reasonably sized boobs)... So heres a lil something to make them nordic women look little
more formidable.

Just to clear up... This is only the normal map along with cleaned up body texture from 
the dirt. It works on ALL human races... 

I WILL make those for beast races too, don\'t have ETA yet though...

To install:
Copy the \"textures\" folder from the zip file to your Data directory of the game, and voila. 

If you want to use it with nude patch... Install it, copy all the files... Then install my mod 
overwriting all the textures that you are asked about.
